---
By: William Gerber
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 454
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
To live is to suffer; that we suffer is, at least in large part, our own
fault; there is a way to eliminate suffering; the way is open to all; the way
to eliminate suffering is to eliminate attachment.
